Package: kworb
Type: Package
Title: Spotify Streaming Data from Kworb.net
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Pete", "O",
      email = "pete@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Scrape and analyze Spotify streaming data from kworb.net.
    Includes functions for downloading daily/weekly charts, individual
    track histories with per-country breakdowns, and building projection
    models for future streams.
